{"tid":1950044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保險問題 今次武漢肺炎有無得賠","createTime":"2020-03-30T05:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T08:43:22.000Z","uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c2e42455faec4f4700adcadf8fb02d56cb2064","tid":1950044,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"例如醫療 人壽 等等 係唔係一般天災 戰爭 暴動 都無得賠 瘟疫包唔包"},{"pid":"799573ba31e19ccb813f97fdd863143f5cce014c","tid":1950044,"uid":68132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:36:38.000Z","msg":"人壽應該有？人都香咗，點都有得賠啦"},{"pid":"3e27f921d96b8d7e50870bfacf35c8fa93b4817a","tid":1950044,"uid":30119,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"人壽: 有得賠<br />\n醫療: 有得賠, 但係武漢肺炎要入公立醫院, 而且講左係免費醫, 所以用唔著<br />\n同埋大部分保險公司而家都有武漢肺炎嘅住院現金<br />\n<br />\n利申: AXA agent"},{"pid":"fcfcdaf07ff849144ef2de5d04725f3035a60496","tid":1950044,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e27f921d96b8d7e50870bfacf35c8fa93b4817a","tid":1950044,"uid":30119,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"人壽: 有得賠<br />\n醫療: 有得賠, 但係武漢肺炎要入公立醫院, 而且講左係免費醫, 所以用唔著<br />\n同埋大部分保險公司而家都有武漢肺炎嘅住院現金<br />\n<br />\n利申: AXA agent"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:03:50.000Z","msg":"入公立唔係都有住院現金賠咩"},{"pid":"cb1126ff95d711967c7278f929874efe5df9407a","tid":1950044,"uid":30119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcfcdaf07ff849144ef2de5d04725f3035a60496","tid":1950044,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e27f921d96b8d7e50870bfacf35c8fa93b4817a","tid":1950044,"uid":30119,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"人壽: 有得賠<br />\n醫療: 有得賠, 但係武漢肺炎要入公立醫院, 而且講左係免費醫, 所以用唔著<br />\n同埋大部分保險公司而家都有武漢肺炎嘅住院現金<br />\n<br />\n利申: AXA agent"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:03:50.000Z","msg":"入公立唔係都有住院現金賠咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"你有買住院現金就有得賠"},{"pid":"aefc7d3279028af00b38b7adbb17dd9c7859e2b4","tid":1950044,"uid":49724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"剩中武漢肺炎的話<br />\n計危疾條款無得賠<br />\n但香港各大保險公司正常都加左武肺附加條款<br />\n其中友邦額外會賠1.5萬<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200131/s00002/ad4a0f4fe9f5e40a6772971df5966e44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200131%2Fs00002%2Fad4a0f4fe9f5e40a6772971df5966e44.jpg&h=f7147b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁中左武肺都有幾個情況<br />\n唔係一黎就死<br />\n以下舉幾個例子<br />\n1. 輕症, 好快出院<br />\n只賠附加條款, 詳見上圖<br />\n2. 重症, 有器官衰竭<br />\n器官衰竭正常會hit到危疾條款, 可以賠到危疾保額+武肺附加條款, 睇agent功力<br />\n3. 死左<br />\n賠武肺附加條款+人壽保額<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題隨便問<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/halahalamiiii\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhalahalamiiii&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2QKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=14c45fcb\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/halahalamiiii</a>"},{"pid":"09288b54a309cc56c49f21fc0170bb09921072a8","tid":1950044,"uid":103445,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a3c2e42455faec4f4700adcadf8fb02d56cb2064","tid":1950044,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"例如醫療 人壽 等等 係唔係一般天災 戰爭 暴動 都無得賠 瘟疫包唔包"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db5e89df676530369ec6998cf1118d83ca0d164","tid":1950044,"uid":30119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09288b54a309cc56c49f21fc0170bb09921072a8","tid":1950044,"uid":103445,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a3c2e42455faec4f4700adcadf8fb02d56cb2064","tid":1950044,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"例如醫療 人壽 等等 係唔係一般天災 戰爭 暴動 都無得賠 瘟疫包唔包"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:1